AGRICULTURE CODE

requirement of destruction of organic cotton. If time is reasonably
available for the production of an economically feasible alternative
crop, the board may require mitigation of losses with the production
of an alternative crop.
Added by Acts 1993, 73rd Leg., ch. 8, Sec. 1, eff. June 1, 1993.
Amended by Acts 1995, 74th Leg., ch. 227, Sec. 19, eff. Sept. 1,
1995; Acts 1997, 75th Leg., ch. 463, Sec. 1.23, eff. May 30, 1997.

